Package io.tarantool.driver.mappers

Interface MessagePackValueMapper

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MessagePackMapper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractResultMapper, CallResultMapper, DefaultMessagePackMapper, DefaultMultiValueResultMapper, DefaultSingleValueResultMapper, TarantoolResultMapper
    public interface MessagePackValueMapper
    Basic interface for collection of generic converters between MessagePack entities and Java objects. Value converters must be added using the registerValueConverter(ValueType, Class, ValueConverter) method
